title: Falling Edge Scope Capture (201h to 200h)
summary: Oscilloscope screenshot of a falling-edge DAC transition with LDAC clock feed-through under 2.5 V reference.

structured_data.description: VOUT trace shown at 1 mV/div and LDAC trigger at 5 V/div. Transition annotated from code 201h to 200h. Feed-through and settling are visible after the edge.
